00:13:35.590 --> 00:13:37.266
If a tiny person
stamps their foot.

271
00:13:37.300 --> 00:13:38.518
does it make a sound?

272
00:13:38.551 --> 00:13:40.895
-Once again. funny.

273
00:13:40.928 --> 00:13:43.239
-Just thoughts. Okay.

274
00:13:44.390 --> 00:13:46.442
I think I know
what I'm gonna do.

275
00:13:46.476 --> 00:13:48.453
