406
00:20:15.364 --> 00:20:19.376
H-hat equals H-bar omega
times A-dagger A

407
00:20:19.410 --> 00:20:23.380
plus one half plus...

408
00:20:23.414 --> 00:20:25.299
[clears throat]

409
00:20:25.332 --> 00:20:30.221
plus P-hat squared
over two M plus two

410
00:20:30.254 --> 00:20:32.223
