411
00:20:32.256 --> 00:20:34.733
uh. X squared. which...

412
00:20:41.557 --> 00:20:42.533
which...

413
00:20:45.770 --> 00:20:49.206
[dramatic music playing]

414
00:21:01.368 --> 00:21:02.553
