434
00:22:59.904 --> 00:23:02.006
Fuck. I fuckin' hate
tape measures.

435
00:23:03.699 --> 00:23:05.376
[grunts]

436
00:23:05.409 --> 00:23:07.836
Okay. [exhales]

437
00:23:07.870 --> 00:23:12.558
