470
00:24:57.479 --> 00:24:59.239
General Henderson:
Let's talk numbers.

471
00:24:59.273 --> 00:25:00.374
Yeah.

472
00:25:04.987 --> 00:25:08.132
[quirky music playing]

473
00:25:11.285 --> 00:25:12.553
-Oh. no. you didn't.

474
00:25:14.455 --> 00:25:17.424
