475
00:25:17.458 --> 00:25:19.852
Fuck. I fuckin' hate
tape measures.

476
00:25:20.219 --> 00:25:22.513
-[gasps]
-It is time you knew the truth

477
00:25:22.546 --> 00:25:24.932
