Les: No. it's not the corn.

484
00:25:39.563 --> 00:25:40.989
Uh. somebody emailed something.

485
00:25:41.023 --> 00:25:43.450
Something not good.
uh. to a journalist.

486
00:25:43.484 --> 00:25:45.202
