in situations such as this.

511
00:26:38.122 --> 00:26:41.008
Now...tell Vivian.

512
00:26:41.041 --> 00:26:42.559
-Um...

513
00:26:44.419 --> 00:26:47.606
-Fine.
Doesn't matter who.

514
00:26:48.924 --> 00:26:52.394
Sometimes.
when someone threatens

515
00:26:52.427 --> 00:26:55.522
