519
00:27:06.984 --> 00:27:10.629
You are going
to have to stop them.

520
00:27:12.781 --> 00:27:14.374
Does that scare you?

521
00:27:14.408 --> 00:27:18.212
-No. Yes. No. Uh. a little.

522
00:27:18.245 --> 00:27:20.881
